The "browser" edition (default) requires:

- McPixel_1372117132.tar.gz
- flash-player-plugin

Note: you can pick the web browser of your choice by running the SlackBuild like
this (example):

BROWSER=google-chrome mcpixel.SlackBuild

Default value is "firefox".

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The "air" edition requires

- mcpixel-linux-air-final.zip
- adobe-air-sdk (available at ftp://someslack.myftp.org/builds/adobe-air-sdk)
- multilib (Slackware64)

To install the air edition, run the SlackBuild with EDITION=air.

To setup multilib, visit:
http://alien.slackbook.org/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=slackware:multilib
